# Dispute_Management_SAP_Automation-Microsoft_Power_Automate
This bot is designed to handle the disputes received from the Chat Bot. The bot has to create the dispute for the provided invoice numbers in SAP and clear the DEBIT / CREDIT records available for the invoice numbers and upload the relevant documents received in input email.
